    <h1>Boeing (BA)<br/>Intrinsic Value</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">A discounted cash flow valuation modeling Boeing's potential turnaround. Using normalized assumptions to find fair value through the turbulence.</p>
    <p class="date">Updated March 18, 2026 · Data: FY2025 Financials</p>
    <p class="compiled-by">Compiled by Gemini 2.5 Pro</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <!-- ═══ THE VERDICT ═══ -->
